+(JNIEnv *env, jobject inObject)
+{
+    __block BOOL ret = NO;
+    JNF_COCOA_ENTER(env);
+    [ThreadUtilities performOnMainThreadWaiting:YES block:^(){
+        ret = [[CClipboard sharedClipboard] checkPasteboardWithoutNotification:nil];
+    }];
+
+    JNF_COCOA_EXIT(env);
+    return ret;
+}
